{
  "stem": "4570.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there must have been some news reels, because I wasn't in that-- I mean, I lived in the city, but not where-- where the tanks and everything came, so-- but I must have seen it in the news reel, because I remember when all the tanks and-- and the armies and everything was marching down [NON-ENGLISH], which is [NON-ENGLISH] place.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and there were a lot of people cheering.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You wouldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and there's a lot of people with-- with-- with swastikas with little flags.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So there were quite a few people who thought that it would be lovely.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they must have been, obviously, German people, because the Czechs certainly never liked the Germans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I-- I don't like the Czech people very much.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they-- they always bow to everybody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're very servile.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as soon as-- as the-- the Nazis were there, they were, you know-- I don't want to say [LAUGHS] what I wanted to say.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were bowing to them, and-- and like they did later on to the communist.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They-- they go with anybody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we couldn't go out together unless-- unless he covered his star, or-- or-- we-- my mother-- I could not remember that my mother ever put a star on.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't think that you sort of went walking in the street.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You only went out, I mean, when you did shopping, or-- or for necessary things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I might have walked with him to where-- where he was living.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I can't ever remember, even before this started, the three of us were, you know, going for a walk or something.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We did that when I was a little child, but not later on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody knew I'm a Jew.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
